Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥殿下独自背负着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却依旧拼死奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心念蕾奥殿下 赶到最前线的米露茜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过星咏所看到的未来无法改变么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去蕾奥殿下和公主殿下就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是 这附近的土地神大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你应该听达尔琪安提起过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那是很久以前就被封印在地下的不祥魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是令人恐怖的大魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那孩子 在哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥殿下 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 米露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这家伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就把你救出来的话 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}蕾奥殿下！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 要逃走么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲卫队长 勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被那魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 米露茜公主殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下大概正被那个魔物禁锢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过圣剑的守护之力还未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是取决于公主殿下的元气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能一直撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主的元气消失之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被那魔物吞噬掉么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能让它发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持圣剑的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子对你们做了这么过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它越走越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以把悬浮的岩石当作踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就可以用托里奈塔滑翔过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在弗洛尼亚的守护之力已经很弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去的话就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 不掉下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托里奈塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先去营救公主殿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要连续跳跃和闪避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来集中精力操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击和防御就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是亲卫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就像平常的铁人运动比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑 跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最短距离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲向终点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然轮不到我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这么快的速度你不会害怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 怕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 比起这些许的胆怯和微小的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辜负他人的期待更加令我难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那些相信我 等待着我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们伤心的话要比现在痛苦上一亿倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者 飞行元气不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 能够到达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让它到达的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你到达的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用纹章炮把你打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会追上来 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾为了让我快走 把我送了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人相信并且等待着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到决赛场地来为我加油的 爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命为我鼓劲的 珍贵的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对我说「你一定能赢的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那天的我没能成为那个温柔女孩的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 也一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是几百年之前的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陆基本还是没被人类划分的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我的孩子是在山间平静地生活的土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与雷光一起劈下的刀将我孩子的身体贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子随即化身为不祥之物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被那孩子囚禁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子作为魔物 吞食山中生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏大地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到200年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在将要袭击人类村庄之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被圣剑的主人亲手封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是因为封印减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是被您的圣剑气息所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子已成为四处破坏的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 成为魔物之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就一直在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 好难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来 谁能来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我死去 杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持圣剑的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以把我那化为魔物的孩子杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用那圣剑斩下这孩子的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 魂魄就会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能维持魔物的姿态了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法摸到这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再让我的孩子如此痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持圣剑的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里杀掉这孩子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许魔物会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 因不断犯下罪恶而加深的悲伤不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是你还是这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么漫长的岁月里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了多少痛苦和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞利多和帕拉迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是降伏魔物之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但更是引导人们生命 孕育大地的希望之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 你们也是弗洛尼亚鲁多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能带着妖刀留下的悲伤就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情 我是绝对不会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝领主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜欧莱{\fnsinhei}·{\r}F{\fnsinhei}·{\r}比斯科帝绝不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拯救这个魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子本是普通的土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把插在身上的红色妖刀拔出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那公主殿下就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…就这样去么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞利多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞利多 是在叫我们加油么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的 所以请借给我些力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神{\fnsimhei}·{\r}圣——之{\fnsimhei}·{\r}刃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 这里就让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地在… 这下不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 真红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔阵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪光波！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那一箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 毫无疑问 就是蕾奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 把那孩子放到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我要用勇者超特急离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
